Keller Williams Realty Of The Treasure Coast

data.description: Welcome to the Florida lifestyle. This 2 bedroom 2 bath is 1300+ Sq Ft Under Air and is located in the highly desirable, no HOA community of Coral Gardens. This bungalow has all of the updates one would want with a plethora of insurance discounts. 2020 Metal Roof with new insulation, 2024 Hot water heater, 2022 HVAC, New gutters, Hurricane impact windows, hurricane doors, and hurricane garage, complete shutters, all *newer* SS Whirlpool kitchen appliances, with soft close wooden cabinets, custom bookshelves with Frank Lloyd Wright glass doors, primary bathroom is fully renovated with rain shower, top of the line finishes, beautiful marble tile, Guest bathroom renovated 2024, Bamboo flooring in primary room and guest room. Brand new fans throughout. Excellent wind-mit & 4 point report 2023. Lush and private fenced in backyard with pond view. Exterior was freshly painted in 2023.  Bring your boat, toys, pets and more! Quick access to I95 and US1 . Don't miss this beautiful opportunity to purchase this well maintained home minutes from the beach, restaurants and more. See features list.
